Four men have been killed in a vigilante attack in Zandspruit in Johannesburg. Five others have been critically injured and are receiving care in the hospital. eNCA's Masego Rahlaga is following this story. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The mother of one of the victims of the alleged vigilante attack in Zandspruit says she is heartbroken at her son's death. The community allegedly burned and killed the deceased and three others on Wednesday morning, while five others were badly injured. READ: Four killed in alleged mob justice attack in Zandspruit Patricia Seabi says her son died in a shameful state.